{
  "stem": "22047.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- I think I was talking about the-- what we did during the three weeks we were at sea.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we were dodging U-boats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and during the day, when we weren't resting or reading or something, I was with my particular troops.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would-- we would talk about what's going to happen in combat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had our exercises.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to exercise.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had classes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't fire any weapons, but we went through book-wise what kinds of operations we might expect to be involved with.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Obviously, in Europe, there was going to be fighting in cities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There would be combat in open field areas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we talked about that a lot, what we would expect.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we would have formations and lectures.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we saw films of news, news broadcasts [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on board ship, and tried to occupy ourselves really in not getting heavily involved in the combat situation, because we didn't want to get so antsy about it that we were all worn out before we got there.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So part of the time was relaxation, a lot of time in eating when we weren't seasick-- and I fortunately wasn't most of the trip-- and reading and we had movies.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every evening, there was a movie shown aboard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a-- played cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a relatively pleasant trip, except the stormy portion of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we never were attacked by any U-boats.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Besides knowing that there's a military war going on, did you know that there was another war going on in Hitler's political party?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Within Germany, you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, that Hitler was going in one direction and the other part of the country was going in another direction.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
